---
title: Popover
---
script(type='module' src='../../js/ce/ux-chi-ce/ux-chi-ce.esm.js')
script(nomodule='' src='../../js/ce/ux-chi-ce/ux-chi-ce.js')

- var sides = ['top', 'right', 'bottom', 'left'];
- var moreSides = ['top', 'top-start', 'top-end', 'right', 'right-start', 'right-end', 'bottom', 'bottom-start', 'bottom-end', 'left', 'left-start', 'left-end'];

.test-base(style='width: 220px; height: 220px;', data-cy="test-base")
  span.-text--h2 Base
  div.-position--relative
    chi-popover(active, title="Popover Title", variant="text")
      | Popover content.

each side in sides
  div(class=`test-${side}`, style='width: 330px; height: 220px;', data-cy=`test-${side}`)
    span.-text--h2=`Simple side ${side}`
    .-position--relative
      chi-popover(position=side, title="Popover Title", variant="text", active, arrow)
        | Popover content.

each side in moreSides
  div(class=`test-more-${side} -position--relative`, data-cy=`test-more-${side}`)
    span.-text--h2=`Popper side ${side}`
    .-d--flex.-justify-content--center.-align-items--center(style="margin: 120px 220px;")
      button(id=side).chi-button Popover
    chi-popover(position=side, title="Popover Title", variant="text", arrow, reference=`#${side}`, active)
      | Popover content.

div(class=`test-with-custom-content -position--relative`, style='width: 450px; height: 320px;', data-cy=`test-with-custom-content`)
  span.-text--h2=`Popover with custom content`
  .-position--relative
    chi-popover(position="top", title="Are you sure?", variant="text", active, arrow, prevent-auto-hide)
      | Are you sure you want to delete this?
      chi-button(slot="chi-popover__footer" color="danger") Delete
      chi-button(slot="chi-popover__footer") Cancel

div(class=`test-closable -position--relative`, style='width: 450px; height: 320px;', data-cy=`test-closable`)
  span.-text--h2=`Popover closable`
  .-position--relative
    chi-popover(title='Popover title', variant='text', closable, active)
      | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.
